<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mentoria das Startups — Luiz de Castro</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --brand: #0B3D2E;
    --brand-mid: #1A6B4A;
    --brand-light: #2FA06D;
    --accent: #F4C842;
    --accent-dark: #C9A020;
    --text: #0D1B13;
    --text-muted: #4A5E53;
    --bg: #F7F5EE;
    --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
    --border: rgba(11,61,46,0.12);
    --radius: 14px;
    --radius-lg: 22px;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(247,245,238,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--brand);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--brand-light); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--brand-mid); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 9rem 2.5rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 80% 30%, rgba(47,160,109,0.13) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 15% 80%, rgba(244,200,66,0.10) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, var(--brand) 0px, var(--brand) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 60px),
                      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand) 0px, var(--brand) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 60px);
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 720px; }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(11,61,46,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(11,61,46,0.15);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--brand-mid);
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero-tag::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--brand-light); animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:0.5;transform:scale(0.8)} }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.5vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--brand);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--brand-light); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .hero-cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 1rem 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(11,61,46,0.25);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--brand-mid); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(11,61,46,0.3); }
  .btn-primary svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
  .btn-secondary {
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-light);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--brand); }

  /* STATS STRIP */
  .stats-strip {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0;
  }
  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 3rem;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }
  .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.8;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
  .section-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--brand-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--brand);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* MODULES GRID */
  .modules-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .module-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .module-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: var(--brand-light);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .module-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(11,61,46,0.1); border-color: rgba(11,61,46,0.2); }
  .module-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .module-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    background: rgba(47,160,109,0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .module-num {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--brand-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .module-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand); margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .module-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .module-meta {
    display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .badge {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(11,61,46,0.07);
    color: var(--brand-mid);
  }
  .badge-accent { background: rgba(244,200,66,0.2); color: #8a6800; }

  /* INCLUDES */
  .includes-section { background: var(--brand); }
  .includes-section h2, .includes-section .section-tag { color: #fff; }
  .includes-section .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .includes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .include-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .include-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.11); }
  .include-icon {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .include-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .include-desc {
    font-size: 0.87rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* MENTOR */
  .mentor-section {
    background: #fff;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .mentor-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .mentor-visual {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,61,46,0.06) 0%, rgba(47,160,109,0.12) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .mentor-avatar {
    width: 100px; height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--brand);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  }
  .mentor-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--brand);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .mentor-title-small {
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400;
  }
  .mentor-text {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-list { max-width: 720px; }
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .faq-question {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .faq-question .toggle {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(11,61,46,0.08);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--brand-light);
    transition: transform 0.25s, background 0.2s;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .faq-item.open .toggle { transform: rotate(45deg); background: var(--brand-light); color: #fff; }
  .faq-answer {
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75;
    max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.35s ease, margin-top 0.25s;
  }
  .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; margin-top: 0.85rem; }

  /* CTA FINAL */
  .cta-final {
    background: var(--brand);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 7rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-final::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  .cta-final::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 900px; height: 900px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  .cta-final-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .cta-final h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-final p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .btn-accent {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--brand);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 1.1rem 2.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(244,200,66,0.35);
  }
  .btn-accent:hover { background: #f8d45f; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(244,200,66,0.45); }
  .free-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(244,200,66,0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(244,200,66,0.35);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--text);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  footer a:hover { color: #fff; }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; }
    .hero { padding: 8rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
    .stat-item { padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .mentor-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .cta-final { padding: 5rem 1.25rem; }
  }

  /* ANIMATION */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="https://www.lojasdecastro.com.br" target="_blank">Luiz de <span>Castro</span></a>
  <a class="nav-cta" href="https://luizdecaxtro.github.io/mentoria_startups/startup-inscricao.html" target="_blank">Inscrever-se grátis</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">100% Online · Gratuito · Certificado oficial</div>
    <h1>Transforme sua ideia em uma <em>startup de sucesso</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Do zero ao empreendedor global — aprenda ideação, modelagem, financeiro, captação de investimento e expansão com mentoria de Luiz de Castro, Mestre em Gestão.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta-group">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="https://luizdecaxtro.github.io/mentoria_startups/startup-inscricao.html" target="_blank">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M10 3v14M3 10l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
        Fazer inscrição gratuita
      </a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#modulos">Ver os módulos ↓</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats-strip">
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">5</span><span class="stat-label">Módulos</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">48</span><span class="stat-label">Aulas</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">+32h</span><span class="stat-label">Conteúdo</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">7</span><span class="stat-label">PDFs</span></div>
  <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">MIA</span><span class="stat-label">IA co-mentora</span></div>
</div>

<!-- MÓDULOS -->
<section id="modulos">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-tag">Programa completo</p>
    <h2>5 Módulos do zero ao sucesso</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Uma jornada progressiva e aplicada, cobrindo tudo que um empreendedor precisa para construir uma startup sólida.</p>
    <div class="modules-grid">
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">💡</div>
        <p class="module-num">Módulo 1</p>
        <p class="module-title">Ideação & Validação</p>
        <p class="module-desc">Design Thinking, MVP, Customer Discovery, Mom Test, pivot vs. perseverar. Valide sua ideia antes de investir tempo e dinheiro.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">6 aulas</span>
          <span class="badge">3h 20min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">Iniciante</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">🏗️</div>
        <p class="module-num">Módulo 2</p>
        <p class="module-title">Modelagem & Registro</p>
        <p class="module-desc">Business Model Canvas, proposta de valor, ICP, tipos societários (LTDA vs S.A.), tributação e propriedade intelectual.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">12 aulas</span>
          <span class="badge">7h 55min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">Iniciante</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">💰</div>
        <p class="module-num">Módulo 3</p>
        <p class="module-title">Financeiro & Marketing</p>
        <p class="module-desc">CAC, LTV, MRR, churn, burn rate, runway, projeções financeiras, growth hacking AARRR, funil de vendas e Customer Success.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">12 aulas</span>
          <span class="badge">8h 30min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">Intermediário</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">📈</div>
        <p class="module-num">Módulo 4</p>
        <p class="module-title">Captação & Operações</p>
        <p class="module-desc">Ecossistema de VCs, pitch deck dos 10 slides, valuation, term sheet, OKRs, LGPD e como construir times de alta performance.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">12 aulas</span>
          <span class="badge">9h 05min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">Avançado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">🌍</div>
        <p class="module-num">Módulo 5</p>
        <p class="module-title">Expansão & Crescimento</p>
        <p class="module-desc">Internacionalização, parcerias estratégicas, M&A, IPO, inovação contínua e o legado do empreendedor.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">6 aulas</span>
          <span class="badge">3h 30min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">Avançado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-card fade-up">
        <div class="module-icon">🏆</div>
        <p class="module-num">Conclusão</p>
        <p class="module-title">Avaliação & Certificado</p>
        <p class="module-desc">Avaliação final com 30 questões. Nota mínima 7,0. Certificado gerado automaticamente ao ser aprovado.</p>
        <div class="module-meta">
          <span class="badge">30 questões</span>
          <span class="badge">60 min</span>
          <span class="badge-accent badge">3 tentativas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INCLUDES -->
<section class="includes-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-tag" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)">Recursos exclusivos</p>
    <h2>O que está incluído</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Além do conteúdo em vídeo e texto, você tem acesso a recursos que aceleram seu aprendizado.</p>
    <div class="includes-grid">
      <div class="include-card fade-up">
        <span class="include-icon">🤖</span>
        <p class="include-title">MIA — IA co-mentora 24h</p>
        <p class="include-desc">Assistente inteligente disponível em todos os módulos para tirar dúvidas, aprofundar conceitos e criar exercícios práticos sob medida.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="include-card fade-up">
        <span class="include-icon">📄</span>
        <p class="include-title">7 PDFs com conteúdo profundo</p>
        <p class="include-desc">Material de apoio para cada módulo, glossário com +80 termos e manual do aluno completo. Ideal para revisão antes da avaliação.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="include-card fade-up">
        <span class="include-icon">🏆</span>
        <p class="include-title">Certificado oficial automático</p>
        <p class="include-desc">Ao atingir nota 7,0 na avaliação final, seu certificado em formato A4 é gerado automaticamente com nome, data e código de validação.</p>
